# UI Component Guidelines

## ShadCN Components
- Use ShadCN UI components for consistent styling
- Customize components to match the project's design system
- Follow the component documentation for proper usage

## Form Components
- Use controlled components for form inputs
- Implement proper validation and error handling
- Show loading states during form submission
- Provide clear success/error feedback to users

## Layout Components
- Use responsive design principles
- Implement mobile-first approach
- Use Flexbox and Grid for layouts
- Ensure proper spacing and alignment

## Navigation Components
- Implement clear navigation structure
- Show active states for current page
- Handle authentication state in navigation
- Provide breadcrumbs for nested pages

## Media Components
- Implement lazy loading for images
- Use Next.js Image component for optimized images
- Create custom video player for self-hosted videos
- Implement YouTube embeds for YouTube videos

## Data Display Components
- Use appropriate components for data visualization
- Implement loading states for data fetching
- Handle empty states gracefully
- Provide clear error messages for failed data fetching
